{"title":"京剧现代戏人物赞（图片）","authors":["田汉"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":6,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"京剧现代戏人物赞\t    田汉　诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶奶和铁梅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔《革命自有后来人》，黑龙江省哈尔滨市京剧团演出〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三家两代一灯存，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨相依即祖孙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送到北山机密件，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来人更党人魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿老　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老　庆　奎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔《箭杆河边》，北京实验京剧团演出〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"箭杆河中水怒流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙沉刀鞘几春秋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庆奎炯眼明如火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤醒麻痹对血仇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈今言　画"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}